# Private workshop repo. Your work (the books, the vault's raw reference ore, and
# the mdBook build output) is ALL versioned and pushed from here for durability.
#
# This file is reserved for surgical exclusions of specific parts of the raw folders
# as needed (e.g. one oversized binary inside a vault source). It is NOT for hiding
# your work. Everything below is deliberately out because it is not your work; flip
# any line if you disagree.

# Secrets: never commit API keys.
.env
**/.env

# Local agent + tooling state (machine-specific, regenerable; gstack is off-limits
# per global instructions).
.claude/
.gstack/

# Python bytecode caches (regenerate on every run; nothing to back up).
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.pytest_cache/

# Multi-book site output: platform/bin/build-site regenerates public/ from the
# committed per-book book/ dirs on every Vercel deploy. Duplicate, not source.
/public/
